### User API Endpoints

# Get all users
GET https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/user/
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Get user by ID (replace {id} with actual user ID)
GET https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/user/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Create a new user
POST https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/user/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstname": "John",
    "lastname": "Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "password123"
}

